Data model

Here is the clean formal object model.

1. Semantic Object Specification (SOS)

The parsed meaning-object.

SOS {
  object_class
  attributes
  relational_constraints
  affordances
  narrative_tags
  priority_invariants
}

Example:
	•	object_class: castle
	•	attributes: ruined, stone, wind-beaten
	•	relational_constraints: on hill, west of village
	•	affordances: enterable, climbable
	•	narrative_tags: ancient frontier defense
	•	priority_invariants: traversable, landmark, visible silhouette

