Dragonfly — perspective shifter

Dragonfly manages view-dependent translation.

A castle seen from afar is not the same representation as one entered from inside.

Dragonfly helps with:
	•	level of detail changes
	•	camera-conditioned enhancement
	•	anticipatory prefetching
